{"tid":2065348,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳： 手足力撐《孤城淚》挑戰票房紀錄 - 李八方","createTime":"2020-06-15T13:20:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T16:38:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"06551587ca74f82098c2a0076410caccaf7fa071","tid":2065348,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T13:20:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200615/OCMHOIGOVBLRRD7ARGXNNBT6AE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200615%2FOCMHOIGOVBLRRD7ARGXNNBT6AE%2F&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7u9tl09raJ%2B2zMWOssuGUT0%3D&h=d276983c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200615%2FOCMHOIGOVBLRRD7ARGXNNBT6AE%2F&h=d7da1537\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200615/OCMHOIGOVBLRRD7ARGXNNBT6AE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：<br />\n手足力撐《孤城淚》挑戰票房紀錄 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SRMFHNMIU4H35IDHSXLKY5BA2I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSRMFHNMIU4H35IDHSXLKY5BA2I.jpg&h=fba7c5bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n法國電影《孤城淚》在港票房有望累收超過300萬。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n香港人同暴政誓不兩立，仲成為全球對抗中共極權嘅橋頭堡，抗爭手足輸出革命，抗爭手法為外國示威活動帶嚟唔少啟發，唔只令國際對香港人另眼相看，仲等大家同國際社會真connect。<br />\n<br />\n喺呢個非常時期，講述05年法國騷亂嘅電影《孤城淚》（Les Miserables）喺。。。。。。。。。。。。已經累收300萬票房，有望成為香港史上票房第六高嘅法語電影。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n目標超越300萬<br />\n<br />\n雖然《孤城淚》法國合資者兼發行商Le Pacte無直接明示支持香港抗爭，但曾經講過，香港嘅抗爭運動係為咗爭取自由；。。。。。。。。。。。。，所以連登有巴打呼籲，香港手足要繼續幫海外手足，總之行動目標，就係要令《孤城淚》香港票房超過300萬。<br />\n<br />\n法國政府文化部嘅旗下機構UniFrance，呢個周末就喺Twitter出帖，話《孤城淚》喺香港票房成功，已經成為自2012年嘅《星光夢裏人》同《閃亮人生》後，香港票房最高嘅法國電影，亦畀國際見到香港嘅「黃色經濟圈」真係有料到。"},{"pid":"4b99548de00b4eaa3af2451ff87e86602addba01","tid":2065348,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T16:38:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}